          </div><div
            class='flex items-center w-full h-[34vh] text-[2.4vh] text-center'
          >
            Simple &amp; Authentic village styled home stay. It’s Massive
            coconut farm but with only 3 boutique mud villas with private
            dinning &amp; sit out. Its has huge pump &amp; tank which is unique
            &amp; alternative experience to swimming pools. Kids will enjoy.
            Overall value for the deal.
