          </div><div
            class='flex items-center w-full h-[34vh] text-[2.4vh] text-center'
          >
            Magical experience :) we planned to go to the Tiger reserve but
            basically forgot our plans because of that place and the local
            (crazy) festival happening in town during our stay (mid-March) We
            were the first foreigners to stay here, the owner Ram welcomed us
            with intense care and the indigenous family living there was a
            highlight in itself..
          </div><div
            class='flex items-center h-max justify-center flex-col w-full flex-[1] gap-[2vh]'
          >
