                fill='#34A853'></path><path
                d='M56.281 156.37c-2.756-8.123-4.351-16.827-4.351-25.82c0-8.994 1.595-17.697 4.206-25.82l-.073-1.73L15.26 71.312l-1.335.635C5.077 89.644 0 109.517 0 130.55s5.077 40.905 13.925 58.602z'
                fill='#FBBC05'></path><path
                d='M130.55 50.479c24.514 0 41.05 10.589 50.479 19.438l36.844-35.974C195.245 12.91 165.798 0 130.55 0C79.49 0 35.393 29.301 13.925 71.947l42.211 32.783c10.59-31.477 39.891-54.251 74.414-54.251'
                fill='#EB4335'></path></svg
            >
          </div><div
            class='flex items-center w-full h-[34vh] text-[2.4vh] text-center'
          >
            Very calm place to stay. Food are really good taste as home Food.
            Definitely we will enjoy the atmosphere. Very good connecting place
            to enjoy forest ride of both the states. Super budgeting place for
            economic lovers.
          </div><div
            class='flex items-center h-max justify-center flex-col w-full flex-[1] gap-[2vh]'
          >
            <div class='h-auto overflow-hidden rounded-full w-[4.8vw]'>
              <Image
                src={vasanthTest}
                class='h-full w-full mx-auto object-contain'
